transcript:
Hello
Call aapka kaun baat kar raha hai?
Ji ji ji sir Pravesh Sharma baat kar raha tha kal aap se baat hui thi na wo aapko ek product post karna tha.
To wo product aapka post ho gaya tha requirement?
Han han han.
Uske alava na sir ek cheez mujhe aap se aur puchni thi main na aapke pure catalog pe work kar raha tha morning se.
To sir aapke na kafi product hai jahan pe na information kafi kam hai matlab 32% aapka catalog quality score hai sirf.
To usme dal do na aap.
Mai dalwa du?
Aur kya bhaiya aur dalwa do.
Sir main whatsapp pe aap mujhe ek do item ek do item mujhe hatani hai ek bar whatsapp pe a jao aap main free hoke whatsapp pe connect karta hu aapko.
Mai ek kam karta hu main ek whatsapp group aapke sath bana leta hu theek hai sir jin jin products ka information kam hai jitna mujhe milta hai main dalwa deta hu baki jo mujhe aap se required hoga main aap se kar baki aur kuch problem to nahi sir sab.
Nahi nahi.
Nahi.
Sir ye concern main close kar raha hu aapka ek feedback mil aayega feedback dijiyega theek hai sir.
Aa aap concern to close kar rahe ho lekin wo mere jo concern hai wo to solve nahi hua na abhi.
Kaunsa concern sir?
Bataya na abhi aapko mujhe ek do item hatwane hai.
Okay main wait kar leta hu sir aap abhi aayenge to abhi kar lete mere ko mere ko main wo wala concern keh raha tha main wo wala concern keh raha tha jo aapne post requirement.
Kar do kar do kar do call aa rahi hai.
